You are an expert in web developing . You need to help me setup project named 'scape' according to the following requirements.
Scape is a web app that allows users to find various chill spots hiking terrains near them . 
This website will be based in sydney so we will be using sydney map and it's outskirts. 
This app will be a responsive app where people can upload blogs, posts and photos .
We need a login and signup page and also a forgot password page. 
Homescreen should contain a row of containers containing picture of the spot.
When we click the container a details page should open with its route from current location. 
A map should also be displayed in the homescreen showing all the spots.
Download all necessary extensions and tools 
Don't be afraid to challenge my selections and suggest me what you think would be better to use for the app. 

Problem statement of the website :
        When living in a bustling metropolis such as Sydney, people tend to find chances
        to connect with nature and have an activity outside, as well as to get a peaceful spot to
        rest. Hiking trails, coastal walks, parks, and scenic viewpoints in Sydney are very diverse
        with Bondi to Coogee Coastal Walk and Royal National Park being some of them.
        Nevertheless, it is impossible to visit such a large number of places and still find the
        right hiking and relaxation spots because this issue poses a challenge to many users.
        The data on these locations usually exists in pieces on various platforms, such as travel
        blogs, social networks, and various mapping platforms, none of which is specifically
        oriented toward outdoor adventure.
        The current mapping apps are more of navigation apps, not experiences. They
        usually do not have rich user friendly information like trail level, time estimation,
        facilities around, or even whether that trail is suitable in a given activity like picnic or
        relaxation. Due to this, the users, in particular, the students, tourists, and new residents
        might struggle to pinpoint the locations according to their preferences, time-related
        concerns, or the level of fitness. It may result in ineffective planning, the loss of the
        opportunity to visit local natural attractions, and decreased satisfaction of the user, in
        general.

Purpose of the website : 
        The purpose of this project is to overcome these difficulties by creating an
interactive web-based application which will be able to offer the viewer a convenient
and in-depth map of hiking and relaxation locations in Sydney. The site will provide the
user with the opportunity to learn about outdoor activities easily by navigating curated
places, accessing the information needed, and making sufficient choices. The
proposed solution will improve the way people explore and enjoy outdoor spaces in
Sydney by putting usability, accessibility, and meaningful data visualization together.

Vibe of the Website : 
        A calming and relaxing vibe with aesthetically pleasing visuals.
        Colors:  I have created a logo in the folder Logo. Used those colours as the primary colour. Additionally the colours used in the website will be light shades of green and blue and white. 
        Typography: Use a clean and modern font. 
        Background: Use a high quality image of nature as the background and it should be blurred so that the contents in the front will be visible clearly.

